Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}悔过吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\fs27}{\an8}「12月3日  背后新宿的狼  PART II」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站着不动真是冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小宫给的信？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都住在一幢公寓里了还写信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有只能在信里说出口的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等下再写回信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从早上开始就确认过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经放进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「背后新宿的狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主试映会吗  会是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到了之后就冲刺过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的座位好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有四个并排的座位的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么难得  可以在一个角度不错的位子看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学拍摄的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士还不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}不要哭  还能见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}嗯  即使转世  无论你变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}我一定会把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\fad(0,500)}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  孩子她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  孩子她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好东西呢  暖炉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  我冲了热可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真缓和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没有想去其它地方的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都直接回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回来的巴士里  我呆呆地想着其它事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神时  都已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐看不了悲剧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是看不了  但是不是会很伤心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  即使知道不能一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是选择在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那样的两人很难过  气氛不是也很高涨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是个Happy End的话  也许会有些不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是专业的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得那画面真的漂亮而看得出神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的漂亮  好绝的用色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能拍出那样的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃和岸说过话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想岸同学也许不记得我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山吹高中的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉野屋老师班上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉野屋老师给我们的票子才能来观看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  非常漂亮  是很棒的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞  今后也要努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人站着看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  自己的作品能让这么多人欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学接下来会得到全国首轮放映奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学的话一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想看她的电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了还有影像这一表现手法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫导演的电影会是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍的话  推理加音乐电影比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如犯人一边唱歌一边追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有主人公陷入危机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跳起舞来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经是喜剧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸同学真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝梦想努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来要做什么还无法决定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虾和鳄梨的炸卷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒粉丝豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡萝卜浓汤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉烧土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪鱼乳酪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了好浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装盘装得那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃和沙英也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我开动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪个开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃  很温和的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感真软～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日式风味的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪鱼乳酪  真是绝妙的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家还没有吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家刚才都在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在写小说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一直都在我脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写起来就很有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看物理书？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在课本上乱写乱画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个力作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我还在吃饭中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有片段  不过脑海中有了印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它画出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:08:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个广告还在放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都放了这么多广告了还不发售真是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是不要期待的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看无数次都要佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是鱼  变成饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成牛排  变成土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变回鱼了  真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个作品就选数学书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  用英日字典来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是个超级大作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心不要被老师发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  稍微走开下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差不多也该…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还没有看过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地打电话过来真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我马上就会读的  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐终于拿到情书了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什什什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪一位寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  刚才的电话是编辑打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说编辑部收到了一封Fan Letter  并寄过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？Fan Letter？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「上个月里登载的小说很精彩」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别找了  那里没有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fan Letter还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～  让我看看有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐好厉害  果然是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在还有Fan了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是激动呢  能让大家看到自己的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许只觉得激动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己的作品是能让他人高兴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我现在要开始着手超级大作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为明天做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有水彩课的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好厉害呀  对于我来说太闪耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  昨天的事情不用放在心上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我忘记东西的时候就麻烦你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了岸同学的电影后我一直坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在非常想画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不知道要画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是要画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H4080FF&}{\bord0}12月13日  结束  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  小时候的记忆是从几岁开始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  是智花出生的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受了很大的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幼儿园的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在出生的时候～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在潜水时想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐浮上水面的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「6月8日  圆圆的胡萝卜」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在向阳庄等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必要来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------------------------
